Package com.strandgenomics.imaging.iclient

Provides a API to access AVADIS Enterprise IMG Server.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
ImageSpace The main class representing the Enterprise IMG Server at the client side
ImageSpaceManagement Administrative APIs - to manager projects and users
ImageSpaceWorkflow Service to enable workflow - executing of task/pipeline by the server
 

Class Summary
AcquisitionProfile client side representation of acquisition profile object
Application Represents an application to be executed (scheduled for execution) by the server
Attachment Handle to an attachment of a record
BookmarkFolder client side representation of record bookmarks.
CoercionHelper  
Experiment  
HistoryItem  
ImageSpaceFactory  
ImageSpaceObject Base class for all objects interested in making system call to the imaging system
ImageSpaceSystem The underlying system class defining the APIs needed to support all the ImageSpace objects
Job Represents a handle to a Task submitted to the server
PixelData An pixel-data (raw bitmap image) within a record is uniquely identified by the 4 dimensions - (slices, frames, sites, channels) in addition to its x and y coordinates.
PixelDataOverlay Represents the overlay state of many pixel-data within a record
PixelMetaData  
Project A place holder of many records - may be an administrative unit or biological
Publisher Publisher of applications
Record Remote representation of a record stored in the server
RecordBuilder RecordBuilder is notional record under construction.
Task Handle to long running Task like archiving projects, deleting projects, restoring archived projects etc
Ticket ticket used for uploading data on server.
Tile A tile or rectangular block within a pixel data
User represents a user within the ImageSpace system
VisualOverlay Remote visual overlays
 

Exception Summary
AuthenticationException  
DuplicateRequestException  
IllegalRequestException This exception is thrown when the server receives request for the same archive to upload or if the archive already exist within the server
ImageSpaceException  
InsufficientPermissionException This exception is thrown when one tries to access an API without sufficient access rights
InvalidAccessTokenException  
PermissionException  
QuotaExceededException  
ServerIsBusyException This exception is thrown when server is too busy to accept any more ticketing request
 

Package com.strandgenomics.imaging.iclient Description

Provides a API to access AVADIS Enterprise IMG Server.
